title: Men's Shoe Production for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Three Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1921-1945 (2)--Original Data, 1944-1954 (3)--Original Data, 1953-1956. Data Include Shoes With Part-Leather Uppers And Non-Leather Uppers As Well As Playshoes And Beginning With 1945, Beach Sandles. Source: Bureau Of The Census, Facts For Industry, Series M63-A, Shoes And Slippers (Monthly).

This NBER data series m01100b appears on the NBER website in Chapter 1 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter01.html.
